---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Who's behind Peculiar Engineer."
	pubDate={new Date('June 05 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm Keith — an engineer who writes things down. This site is where I keep the
		guides, install walkthroughs, and runbooks I build while working through real
		problems.
	</p>

	<p>
		I started Peculiar Engineer because I kept solving the same problems twice. Every
		post here is something I actually did: the commands that worked, the errors I hit
		along the way, and the reasoning behind each step — so it's reproducible whether
		you're following along or it's future-me coming back six months later.
	</p>

	<p>
		If a guide saved you some time, or you spot something that's gone stale, feel free
		to reach out. Thanks for stopping by.
	</p>
</Layout>
